WEBVTT

00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:15.120
Nice to see today so many Sahaja yogis
looking like beautiful lotus flowers,

00:00:17.580 --> 00:00:28.620
as the blossom time is filled
with the fragrance of your beauty.

00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:43.200
It is such a pleasure for Me
to be your Mother

00:00:47.460 --> 00:00:55.980
and to be able to communicate the Divine,
the powers of Divine,

00:00:56.880 --> 00:01:00.120
the beauty of Divine to you.

00:01:01.860 --> 00:01:04.620
It was never possible before, as you know.

00:01:05.940 --> 00:01:10.860
Everyone tried their level best
but nobody could achieve it,

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:15.240
to communicate that beauty.

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:24.600
As you know, Sahaja Yoga,
or this Mahayoga is a very unique system,

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:26.580
it never existed before.

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:31.440
It has come into existence,

00:01:34.860 --> 00:01:37.440
of course,
I should say that

00:01:37.980 --> 00:01:44.760
because the Parabrahma decided to take a
form,

00:01:45.300 --> 00:01:50.280
but you also all decided to come

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:52.320
on this earth to receive the blessings.

00:01:54.300 --> 00:02:00.840
It cannot be possible to do anything
with one hand.

00:02:02.580 --> 00:02:05.640
The beauty of Sahaja Yoga is great,
no doubt,

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:12.660
which I am sure very soon people
will realize that this is the only way.

00:02:14.580 --> 00:02:19.380
All lost people will come back
to Sahaja Yog, I'm sure,

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:22.740
and they will achieve what they are due.

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:26.760
You don't have to do anything
about Sahaja Yoga,

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:29.100
you just walk in
and you can get Realization.

00:02:30.900 --> 00:02:33.540
In India there was a gentleman
who came to see Me

00:02:34.620 --> 00:02:37.260
and he told Me a big story about his woes,

00:02:37.260 --> 00:02:42.000
he told Me he's under debt,
he has so many problems,

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:46.500
his wife is like this,
his children are like this,

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:50.700
and he has problems, political problems,
all sorts of problems he had.

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:53.820
And then he got his Realization.

00:02:55.980 --> 00:02:57.780
And he said,
"Mother, what have You done to me?"

00:02:57.780 --> 00:02:58.980
I said, "Why?"

00:02:58.980 --> 00:03:03.840
He said, "I have forgotten all this
and I'm in joy, I am in joy",

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:04.860
you see.

00:03:04.860 --> 00:03:06.780
I said, "It could be an escape."

00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:11.160
He said, "No, I can see all that,
but I am still in joy."

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:14.640
Next time he met Me he said,
"I've solved all my problems,

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:19.260
because I was in joy,
and I could share it with others.

00:03:19.260 --> 00:03:20.940
Things improved a lot."

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:26.640
That's how Sahaja Yoga works,
instantaneously, spontaneously,

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:29.100
without any effort. It's true.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:32.700
But we have to face certain things.

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:39.900
The fact, that we were not so prepared
for Sahaja Yog, in the sense,

00:03:39.900 --> 00:03:48.540
that we are people living in this life
of turmoil, confusion,

00:03:48.540 --> 00:03:50.340
all kinds of funny ideas.

00:03:51.540 --> 00:03:55.560
And idea of dharma is also missing,
it's only in the books

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:59.160
or in the churches maybe somewhere
people talk, only talk.

00:03:59.940 --> 00:04:02.880
It's not actually existing.

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:09.420
Moreover, we have also not got
the traditions left with us,

00:04:09.420 --> 00:04:15.540
which are required to be a person
to worship the Divine.

00:04:17.640 --> 00:04:21.900
Most of our traditions we have lost
because firstly we discovered

00:04:21.900 --> 00:04:29.460
that there's lot of hypocrisy
and insincerity

00:04:29.460 --> 00:04:32.040
as far as religion is concerned.

00:04:32.040 --> 00:04:36.540
The people who talk of religion
behave in such manner

00:04:36.540 --> 00:04:39.060
that you cannot believe that there is God.

00:04:39.060 --> 00:04:41.880
So they denied God,
they denied all the traditions,

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:44.640
they said, "This is all useless,
it has no meaning,

00:04:44.640 --> 00:04:50.280
better give up all the religions,
it's fanaticism, it is nonsense."

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:54.660
Because it did not give them any fruits,
according to them,

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:58.740
they couldn't wait for Sahaja Yoga
to come in to prove

00:04:58.740 --> 00:05:01.440
that all religions are absolutely correct,

00:05:01.440 --> 00:05:07.440
and their traditions are absolutely
necessary if you really want

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:15.120
to have the maximum of the joy
and the beauty of the Divine.

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:20.100
But it so happened, that we lost
those traditions, we've lost,

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:23.160
most of the traditions are lost.

00:05:25.740 --> 00:05:29.640
It is surprising,
how many traditions we have lost

00:05:29.640 --> 00:05:31.320
and we are not aware of it.

00:05:32.100 --> 00:05:37.320
So a new education is needed for us
to understand the traditions

00:05:37.320 --> 00:05:38.880
of worshiping.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:45.840
It's easy to have a puja,
because your Mother is always available.

00:05:47.580 --> 00:05:50.940
If you just tell Her there is puja,
She'll dress up and come down here.

00:05:52.260 --> 00:05:56.880
But in tradition at least there should be
an invitation,

00:05:56.880 --> 00:06:01.260
you have to come, and receive,
and ask for coming,

00:06:01.260 --> 00:06:04.080
because now you see
the joke of the whole thing is.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:06.660
But it's all right, because you
don't know, it's all right.

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:10.380
It's not only that, I'm saying on the
whole,

00:06:10.380 --> 00:06:15.660
a worship is a tradition
which has come to us

00:06:15.660 --> 00:06:18.120
from great seers and ancient sages.

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:25.200
Anybody, even, say, Moses,
you can say Socrates,

00:06:25.200 --> 00:06:32.640
you can say Dattatreya, or Markandeya,
or any one of these people

00:06:33.420 --> 00:06:40.860
have found out the ways and methods
how to tune our instruments to the Divine

00:06:41.520 --> 00:06:43.380
to achieve the maximum joy.

00:06:44.640 --> 00:06:47.700
How to please the Deities,
that's the main point is,

00:06:47.700 --> 00:06:48.960
how to please the Deities.

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:53.760
But it's a crude word "pleases",
but how to…

00:06:58.200 --> 00:07:01.140
I don't know what should I say,
innovation they say,

00:07:01.140 --> 00:07:03.060
or what do you call that?

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:12.240
How to spark them, invoke, invoke them,
invoke them that they give you

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.560
complete blessings.

00:07:14.520 --> 00:07:19.920
And the trick of the trade
one has to learn, one has to educate.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:22.920
There's nothing wrong
in getting educated.

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:26.460
So we know that we have to
educate ourselves, first point,

00:07:26.460 --> 00:07:30.840
and secondly we have to know that
for that we have to be humble.

00:07:32.220 --> 00:07:37.200
The humility should be such that
"I have to learn. I have to learn.

00:07:37.200 --> 00:07:41.280
I have to educate. Nothing wrong in it."

00:07:41.820 --> 00:07:46.200
And I have told you before that
in ancient times the gurus used to be

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:50.580
so strict with their disciples
that they used to put them

00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:58.560
hanging on a well for three days,
before they could enter even

00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.760
into the university.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:07.140
So if they could stand all that insults,
then only they would bring the students

00:08:07.140 --> 00:08:10.740
inside and start talking
about any education.

00:08:12.180 --> 00:08:15.060
Because, you see, in educating a person

00:08:17.340 --> 00:08:23.147
if you have no humility and understanding
that I do not know, I have to know,

00:08:23.147 --> 00:08:28.500
– it's a fact, because this is the new
journey towards the roots, as I said.

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:31.680
You are the roots, Sahaja Yogis are
the roots of the whole universe,

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:32.400
do you know that?

00:08:33.060 --> 00:08:36.240
You are the roots,
and as roots you have to know

00:08:36.240 --> 00:08:44.100
how to journey through this deeper parts
of spiritual life, to grow.

00:08:44.820 --> 00:08:47.550
When you grow deep, the tree grows up.

00:08:47.550 --> 00:08:51.720
It is through you only,
the nourishment of the

00:08:52.380 --> 00:08:56.280
this overgrown universe is going to be
looked after.

00:08:56.280 --> 00:08:59.940
And the more it overgrows,
you must grow deeper.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:04.380
But for that you must have education,
it's important.

00:09:05.460 --> 00:09:10.080
Look at the little cell
at the tip of a root,

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:16.920
how it moves with complete intelligence,
understanding and wisdom.

00:09:19.020 --> 00:09:25.035
Supposing it is hit by a stone,
it doesn't feel bad, it goes back.

00:09:25.035 --> 00:09:28.080
It knows where to recede,
where to go further,

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:32.040
where to go round the thing
and how to use the same stone

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:35.880
for making the tree very strong.

00:09:37.560 --> 00:09:42.420
All this education you have to get
through your experiences

00:09:42.420 --> 00:09:45.300
and by all the time saying humbly:
"I have to learn."

00:09:47.340 --> 00:09:52.440
That is very important,
that we have to have that humility

00:09:53.340 --> 00:09:54.720
to educate ourselves.

00:09:54.720 --> 00:10:03.900
Because with that education you'll embed
this tremendous task into the minds

00:10:03.900 --> 00:10:06.720
of people, which is a very difficult
thing.

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:15.420
The movement is outward in this shoots,
in this outside tree, outward.

00:10:15.420 --> 00:10:19.860
It's easy to impress a person
if you are insincere, very easy –

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:23.640
if you can dress up in a particular way,
smile in a different way,

00:10:23.640 --> 00:10:26.640
look in a different way,
if you can act very well

00:10:26.640 --> 00:10:30.540
you can impress anyone, for the people
who are superficial we say.

00:10:31.800 --> 00:10:37.500
The veneer that we have so far
is not needed any more.

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:43.050
There is no need to have the veneer,
because inside we have found our Self,

00:10:43.050 --> 00:10:46.620
our own Spirit, our own beauty
which is going to flower out,

00:10:46.620 --> 00:10:47.700
which is going to come out.

00:10:47.700 --> 00:10:51.840
So there's no need to have
any artificial veneer at all,

00:10:53.100 --> 00:10:58.200
because I know you
and the Deities know you.

00:10:58.200 --> 00:11:01.260
There is no need to have
any artificiality outside.

00:11:02.280 --> 00:11:05.340
We put on some sort of
an artificial veneer.

00:11:06.420 --> 00:11:09.120
What's the use for us?
Nothing, we are not going to impress

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:12.840
people outwardly.
We have to impress them inwardly.

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:17.580
So for inward growth all this veneer
must drop out.

00:11:17.580 --> 00:11:26.670
The veneer has come through so many
kinds of acceptance of norms and the,

00:11:26.670 --> 00:11:31.080
we can say, the formalities of life
are concerned.

00:11:31.080 --> 00:11:35.280
That veneer is within us:
if you say thank you ten times, finished,

00:11:35.280 --> 00:11:39.300
if you say sorry two times, is all right.

00:11:39.900 --> 00:11:44.280
But from inside to feel something,
to genuinely feel something,

00:11:44.880 --> 00:11:47.880
to be genuine about it is our work.

00:11:50.340 --> 00:11:53.520
But that doesn't mean that we should
have no tradition.

00:11:53.520 --> 00:11:58.080
Tradition gives us that beauty
to grow in a proper way.

00:12:01.080 --> 00:12:06.480
For example, you'll see, we'll find people
talk here sometimes gives you a shock,

00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:09.060
I mean the way
"I'll buy you a lunch today,"

00:12:09.060 --> 00:12:13.800
say, a thing like that.
It's horrible to say such a thing,

00:12:13.800 --> 00:12:16.828
as to say "I'll buy you a lunch today,"
you see.

00:12:16.828 --> 00:12:21.300
It's very rude and crude way of talking,
isn't it?

00:12:21.300 --> 00:12:26.280
On the contrary, it's better to say that
"Will you give me the pleasure

00:12:26.280 --> 00:12:27.900
of you having for lunch?"

00:12:27.900 --> 00:12:31.560
Is no artificiality:
that's the way you should feel it.

00:12:31.560 --> 00:12:34.800
There's no artificiality
because from your heart it is coming,

00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:36.960
you're saying it from your heart.

00:12:36.960 --> 00:12:38.760
But if you are not saying it
from your heart,

00:12:39.540 --> 00:12:43.080
it's better even if you are not saying
with your heart, it's better to say

00:12:43.080 --> 00:12:44.460
that it would be a pleasure.

00:12:44.460 --> 00:12:47.040
Because to say that
"I'll buy you a lunch

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:47.880
and you buy me tomorrow."

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:57.900
To say another thing, you see, it's also
possible, this is, this people think

00:12:57.900 --> 00:13:01.920
is being very open,
and there's no insincerity –

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:03.720
because you are insincere!

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:08.820
Because you are insincere,
that's why you want to avoid insincerity.

00:13:09.540 --> 00:13:10.920
Why not be sincere?

00:13:11.940 --> 00:13:17.760
By saying whatever looks so sincere
is actually vulgar.

00:13:17.760 --> 00:13:20.580
It is not proper to say such a thing.

00:13:20.580 --> 00:13:27.600
But for a Sahaja Yogi if he is traditional
as well as his inner self is shining,

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:31.140
it's like a beautiful diamond
put in a beautiful ring.

00:13:33.060 --> 00:13:37.800
So I feel that an education
in our behavior has to come in.

00:13:37.800 --> 00:13:42.360
Our language has to change.
Our style has to change.

00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:45.300
We have to live in a way
that people should feel

00:13:45.300 --> 00:13:50.400
that these are decent people,
very normal people.

00:13:50.400 --> 00:13:53.520
You don't have to do anything abnormal
to be a Sahaja Yogi.

00:13:54.180 --> 00:14:01.200
You have to be extremely normal, decent
people, who know decent language.

00:14:02.820 --> 00:14:08.340
There is no need to put up any show,
for example, you see, an artificial smile,

00:14:08.340 --> 00:14:12.180
or an artificial face,
there's no need at all.

00:14:13.860 --> 00:14:22.020
For a Sahaja Yogi to become like
any other person is no hypocrisy.

00:14:22.800 --> 00:14:25.380
You see, a Sahaja Yogi may think
"Mother, it's a hypocrisy,

00:14:25.380 --> 00:14:27.300
because I'm a Sahaja Yogi,
I'm a Realized soul,

00:14:27.300 --> 00:14:30.240
why should I dress up like other people,
you see.

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:32.100
It's a hypocrisy." It is not.

00:14:32.100 --> 00:14:36.600
For a king to dress up like a beggar,
is it a hypocrisy?

00:14:37.260 --> 00:14:39.840
Will you call it a hypocrisy? It is not.

00:14:39.840 --> 00:14:44.340
Now, I am a, I am supposing,
I am a Goddess.

00:14:44.340 --> 00:14:47.820
I'm not supposed to dress up
like ordinary people.

00:14:47.820 --> 00:14:51.000
I'm to be decked up all the time,
I should have this, that,

00:14:51.000 --> 00:14:53.700
but I have to dress up
like ordinary person,

00:14:53.700 --> 00:14:59.760
so is it hypocrisy?
Is it hypocrisy by that? It is not.

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:03.600
Hypocrisy is to claim something
that you are not.

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:04.920
It's a higher level.

00:15:04.920 --> 00:15:08.820
You see, supposing a person,
who is not even a realized soul,

00:15:08.820 --> 00:15:11.340
and he says "I am a guru."
Then he is a hypocrite.

00:15:11.880 --> 00:15:16.680
But not a real guru,
behaves like an ordinary person.

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:19.200
Is a question of discretion.
One should understand,

00:15:19.200 --> 00:15:20.700
is a question of discretion.

00:15:20.700 --> 00:15:25.560
So when you dress up like an ordinary
person in an ordinary way

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:30.120
there is no question of hypocrisy.

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:35.280
But maybe you are doing it for a thing
not to appear something so much

00:15:35.280 --> 00:15:36.780
that other's ego is hurt.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:41.400
Actually I do that only
just not to hurt anybody's ego,

00:15:41.400 --> 00:15:42.600
to be very frank.

00:15:42.600 --> 00:15:46.500
I go about like that because I do not want
to hurt anybody's ego,

00:15:46.500 --> 00:15:48.960
because hurting ego means
they'll go down further,

00:15:49.620 --> 00:15:51.900
so maybe that is the reason you are doing,

00:15:51.900 --> 00:15:56.160
for the sake of their good
if you have to take up a dress like that

00:15:56.160 --> 00:15:57.180
– doesn't matter.

00:15:57.960 --> 00:16:01.080
But hypocrisy comes in
when you are not that

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.100
and you claim something.

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:09.720
Now for a Sahaja Yogi it is important
to know that he has to improve.

00:16:09.720 --> 00:16:11.460
He has to go further, he has to grow.

00:16:11.460 --> 00:16:18.780
And for the growth whatever is necessary
must be accepted in right, proper way.

00:16:21.480 --> 00:16:26.400
Now, today is a very auspicious day
that you are celebrating My Birthday.

00:16:27.240 --> 00:16:31.920
I'm sure by the time I'm sixty
years of age you would grow so fast,

00:16:32.760 --> 00:16:39.600
this year I wish that you grow so fast,
that when people see you they should feel

00:16:39.600 --> 00:16:44.880
a great beautiful personality
standing before us,

00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:48.660
each one of you have to be great people,
each one of you.

00:16:49.320 --> 00:16:52.440
For Me, that's the only thing to be seen.

00:16:52.440 --> 00:16:56.460
And it can be accelerated very fast
if you understand you have to learn

00:16:56.460 --> 00:16:59.160
every moment,
the humility is necessary.

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:03.300
If you know that you have to grow
every moment you'll be amazed

00:17:03.300 --> 00:17:05.370
how fast you can grow.

00:17:05.370 --> 00:17:07.140
Every moment you have to change.

00:17:07.680 --> 00:17:12.060
For example, your style of talking,
some people have a style of talking,

00:17:12.060 --> 00:17:15.540
you can see in the mirror,
how would you like a Sahaja Yogi

00:17:15.540 --> 00:17:17.160
to have that kind of a style of talking?

00:17:17.160 --> 00:17:22.020
Some people have a style of, you see,
laughing in a funny way,

00:17:22.020 --> 00:17:23.820
all the time they'll be laughing,
giggling,

00:17:23.820 --> 00:17:26.040
while talking "he-hu" they go on,

00:17:26.040 --> 00:17:28.500
that's not the way a Sahaja Yogi should
be.

00:17:28.500 --> 00:17:32.340
He should be serene,
he should laugh when it is necessary,

00:17:32.340 --> 00:17:36.120
he should smile at when it is necessary.

00:17:36.120 --> 00:17:42.120
It is so much in tune with your Spirit
that whatever you do should create beauty.

00:17:42.120 --> 00:17:47.160
Even when you cry at the time
when it is necessary, it's so beautiful.

00:17:48.300 --> 00:17:52.800
See, tears come into your eyes sometimes,
they do.

00:17:52.800 --> 00:17:58.260
But you see somebody very sick,
somebody very ill, unhappy –

00:17:58.260 --> 00:18:02.820
then the tears should come,
not when something about you is bad.

00:18:02.820 --> 00:18:03.570
That's a Sahaja Yogi.

00:18:03.570 --> 00:18:08.760
The Sahaja Yogi must feel for others,
not for oneself.

00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:11.880
In the same way, when you laugh, you see,
you shouldn't just laugh

00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:14.160
as a matter of habit.

00:18:14.160 --> 00:18:16.440
Some people have a habit,
whenever they talk they start

00:18:16.440 --> 00:18:20.040
with the laughter
or they'll just in between "he",

00:18:20.040 --> 00:18:22.920
they'll say again "he", they'll say
– has no meaning.

00:18:22.920 --> 00:18:28.140
Every time the person who laughs
can be idiotic also,

00:18:28.140 --> 00:18:30.000
so one should not appear that way.

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:35.640
Or one should not be so serious,
that next moment a person wants

00:18:35.640 --> 00:18:37.380
to get away from you
the way you are serious.

00:18:37.380 --> 00:18:41.460
I mean there are silent bores also,
they just bore you by their silence.

00:18:41.460 --> 00:18:45.780
But whatever you have to speak
it should come from your heart.

00:18:45.780 --> 00:18:49.320
If it really comes from your heart,
I tell you,

00:18:49.320 --> 00:18:55.560
it will have so much effect,
because heart gives that beauty to you.

00:18:55.560 --> 00:18:59.400
That's your Spirit.
Connection is with the Spirit.

00:18:59.400 --> 00:19:04.200
When you speak it from your heart,
feelingly, whatever you speak,

00:19:04.200 --> 00:19:09.240
it shows so much of your feelings
on your face, and on your behavior,

00:19:09.240 --> 00:19:11.700
everything, and it touches
another person's heart,

00:19:11.700 --> 00:19:13.620
means you touch the roots of the person.

00:19:14.820 --> 00:19:19.380
You touch the absolute innermost
part of his,

00:19:19.380 --> 00:19:25.200
"antakkarana" as you say,
innermost compartment of his life,

00:19:25.200 --> 00:19:26.880
and from there the light comes.

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:33.240
Now this difference we must understand
that our education now is going to be

00:19:33.240 --> 00:19:37.500
sincerity to speak from your own heart,
and not from outside.

00:19:37.500 --> 00:19:41.340
Now we have all the formalities
how to say it, how to eat,

00:19:41.340 --> 00:19:43.980
these things are very, very superficial
for Sahaja Yoga.

00:19:44.640 --> 00:19:46.560
These are not so important.

00:19:46.560 --> 00:19:48.720
For Sahaja Yoga,
these things do not matter.

00:19:48.720 --> 00:19:52.920
But traditionally those things
that are accepted must be seen,

00:19:52.920 --> 00:19:56.880
discretely used,
and we should behave in such a manner

00:19:56.880 --> 00:20:01.260
that whatever we say from our heart
should have that beautiful cover

00:20:01.260 --> 00:20:03.540
of a tradition. That's all.

00:20:03.540 --> 00:20:08.700
But you need not be artificial at all,
there's no need to be artificial.

00:20:10.020 --> 00:20:15.240
Now the line to draw
between artificiality and reality

00:20:15.240 --> 00:20:17.520
is very difficult for people.

00:20:17.520 --> 00:20:20.040
Because, you see,
if you intellectualize it,

00:20:20.040 --> 00:20:21.720
you can intellectualize everything.

00:20:21.720 --> 00:20:25.260
For example, if I say that
something is wrong with you.

00:20:27.360 --> 00:20:33.120
So you may feel that I have criticized,
or something, you may feel bad.

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:39.600
This is according to his reality,
is not true. It is unreal.

00:20:39.600 --> 00:20:43.740
Because you have come here
to educate yourself, all right?

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:45.300
Now I have to tell you something.

00:20:45.300 --> 00:20:49.200
When I tell you and if you feel hurt
then it is not reality.

00:20:49.200 --> 00:20:52.020
Then what is it?
It is your ego,

00:20:52.680 --> 00:20:55.620
you are playing with your ego,
not with your Spirit.

00:20:55.620 --> 00:21:00.300
On the contrary, a man who has Spirit
will feel happy that

00:21:00.300 --> 00:21:04.740
"I'm in the attention of Mother,
that She can correct me."

00:21:04.740 --> 00:21:09.300
So second is, that to be in the attention
of your Mother.

00:21:09.840 --> 00:21:15.600
Whether She says you're good, bad,
or anything is very important,

00:21:16.140 --> 00:21:17.160
is very important.

00:21:18.360 --> 00:21:22.680
Not to be away from Mother's attention
is very important.

00:21:23.220 --> 00:21:27.360
Because supposing today you might feel
something bad and you may try

00:21:27.360 --> 00:21:30.240
to get out of Her attention,
who will look after you?

00:21:31.140 --> 00:21:33.720
She is looking after you,
She has to correct you

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:38.400
and She has to tell you that this is not
proper and this is not good, this is good.

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:43.500
In that you have to have faith
that you will definitely come up,

00:21:44.040 --> 00:21:48.540
you will have to come up,
because I am interested in you

00:21:48.540 --> 00:21:49.920
I am telling you.

00:21:49.920 --> 00:21:53.340
So to be in the Mother's attention
is very important

00:21:53.340 --> 00:21:57.240
and that Mother's attention
is all the time with you

00:21:57.240 --> 00:22:00.300
till you absolutely try to get out of it.

00:22:00.300 --> 00:22:03.780
Because I cannot force Myself upon you,
that's the main point is,

00:22:03.780 --> 00:22:06.330
I cannot force myself upon you.

00:22:06.330 --> 00:22:10.380
But if you want My attention,
then I have to tell you

00:22:10.380 --> 00:22:14.040
if you are touching something,
say a child is touching this fire,

00:22:14.040 --> 00:22:15.780
won't you tell the child don't do it?

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:19.320
So every moment the Mother
has to look after.

00:22:19.320 --> 00:22:24.780
And She loves you, not only that,
but to Her you're so important.

00:22:25.740 --> 00:22:28.680
I mean, nobody would like to say anything
to anyone these days,

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:32.760
because people want to be popular,
this cheap popularity.

00:22:33.840 --> 00:22:36.780
I'm not a person
who is asking for popularity.

00:22:36.780 --> 00:22:40.500
What I want, that My children should be
beautiful people.

00:22:41.220 --> 00:22:43.560
Then they enter into the Kingdom of God.

00:22:45.180 --> 00:22:51.540
They should be respected as great saints,
sages, more than anybody else.

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:55.620
They're special people and that's how
they have to be educated.

00:22:56.220 --> 00:23:02.400
Maybe I'm very ambitious, you might say,
but My ambitions are based on reality.

00:23:03.060 --> 00:23:05.220
I'm sure I can achieve it.

00:23:05.220 --> 00:23:09.420
But you must develop that,
that humility within yourself,

00:23:09.420 --> 00:23:13.200
and understanding that we all
have to improve,

00:23:13.200 --> 00:23:16.800
we have to be in the attention of Mother,
if She has to say something to us,

00:23:16.800 --> 00:23:18.000
we are not to feel hurt.

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:20.880
If you feel hurt,
then know that it is your ego,

00:23:20.880 --> 00:23:25.560
beat yourself with shoes, take it out,
because is not good.

00:23:25.560 --> 00:23:28.200
I cannot go on pampering your ego
all the time,

00:23:28.200 --> 00:23:31.500
till you're completely blasted off
and then you come and tell Me,

00:23:31.500 --> 00:23:33.180
"Mother why didn't you tell me?"

00:23:33.180 --> 00:23:36.120
For example, somebody asked Me,
he's in love with somebody,

00:23:36.120 --> 00:23:38.280
wants to marry,
I knew the person was horrible

00:23:38.280 --> 00:23:39.420
and he should not marry the person.

00:23:40.800 --> 00:23:42.720
And I said that, in a way.

00:23:43.260 --> 00:23:46.200
I said, "All right."
I mean, at first it was a shock,

00:23:46.200 --> 00:23:48.180
and I kept quiet.
I said, now, how to say,

00:23:49.560 --> 00:23:51.360
not to pamper his ego either.

00:23:51.360 --> 00:23:55.680
But to say, how to say that no?
And yes – it will be very difficult.

00:23:55.680 --> 00:23:58.440
So I said, "All right,
as long as she makes you happy,

00:23:58.440 --> 00:23:59.160
it's all right."

00:23:59.160 --> 00:24:04.560
Now the word "happy" is a double meaning.
"Happy" means only your ego can be happy,

00:24:04.560 --> 00:24:06.420
not the Spirit, is joy.

00:24:06.420 --> 00:24:08.700
I did not use the word "joy",
I said "happy".

00:24:09.300 --> 00:24:11.040
See I have to be clever about it.

00:24:11.040 --> 00:24:14.640
Now, if you have thought of it,
"Why would it Mother say 'happy'?

00:24:14.640 --> 00:24:17.340
She should have said
'If it gives you joy'."

00:24:17.340 --> 00:24:20.280
If I say "joy" then it's correct,
but I said "happy".

00:24:20.820 --> 00:24:25.560
And I said it three-four times to him,
that "Does it make you happy?"

00:24:26.460 --> 00:24:29.100
He said "Yes."
"If it makes you happy, you can marry

00:24:29.100 --> 00:24:29.600
her."

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:34.080
Now, you see, if – he's very intelligent
and he should have thought of it,

00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:37.440
but he never thought of it
that I was meaning that

00:24:37.440 --> 00:24:39.600
it is not going to give you joy,
it will give you,

00:24:39.600 --> 00:24:40.980
"if it gives you happiness, you marry."

00:24:40.980 --> 00:24:46.680
Happiness means: is your ego pampering,
is simple.

00:24:47.220 --> 00:24:50.400
Also you have to educate yourself
to understand your Mother.

00:24:50.940 --> 00:24:55.440
This is the third thing you have to know
is to understand your Mother.

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:59.520
See, I have to be clever,
because if I'm not,

00:24:59.520 --> 00:25:02.760
if I am very blunt you get blasted.

00:25:03.420 --> 00:25:05.340
If I am not, you are lost.

00:25:06.240 --> 00:25:10.440
So I have to be clever,
and when I'm clever they call Me Mahamaya.

00:25:23.880 --> 00:25:28.740
So, at least let Me keep to one style,
let Me be a Mahamaya, all right, accepted.

00:25:28.740 --> 00:25:32.940
But then you try to understand that
if I tell you something,

00:25:32.940 --> 00:25:36.480
you just get absolutely annoyed and angry.

00:25:36.480 --> 00:25:39.420
And people get lost, you see, they get
lost,

00:25:39.420 --> 00:25:42.120
if you tell them "don't do it," they get
lost.

00:25:42.120 --> 00:25:45.780
If you say "do it", then they get lost
in any case because they're doing

00:25:45.780 --> 00:25:48.420
a wrong thing, so it is a big problem,

00:25:48.420 --> 00:25:53.280
and you should see what is good for you,
"svartha".

00:25:53.280 --> 00:25:57.900
"Svartha" also means "selfishness"
but it means "the meaning of yourself".

00:25:58.500 --> 00:26:02.760
"Sva-artha", that's what you
have to find out for yourself,

00:26:02.760 --> 00:26:06.600
what is good for you,
and if Mother is saying something,

00:26:07.680 --> 00:26:10.560
then what is the meaning
of what Mother is saying.

00:26:10.560 --> 00:26:15.240
I'm too simple, but I'm very crooked,
because when I tell you something

00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:20.580
straightforward, you do not understand,
so I have to go in a roundabout way, see,

00:26:20.580 --> 00:26:22.560
that's the diplomacy of Shri Krishna.

00:26:22.560 --> 00:26:29.820
You see, because Mother's intentions are
very simple and sincere

00:26:29.820 --> 00:26:35.940
that My children should grow
into real Divine power.

00:26:36.780 --> 00:26:41.400
They should become really,
actually Divinity.

00:26:42.420 --> 00:26:48.300
They should be nothing but embodiment
of God's love.

00:26:50.220 --> 00:26:55.980
I'm very ambitious,
I have all confidence in Myself,

00:26:57.060 --> 00:27:02.340
in you also,
and I'm sure you will understand,

00:27:02.340 --> 00:27:05.640
that I do not do your ego-pampering.

00:27:05.640 --> 00:27:11.100
I encourage you,
and I also sometimes discourage you.

00:27:11.100 --> 00:27:18.060
Both forces are important
if you have to progress properly.

00:27:18.060 --> 00:27:22.440
So when I encourage you, you feel happy,
means your ego is there.

00:27:22.440 --> 00:27:24.960
When I discourage you,
you feel discouraged,

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:26.820
means your superego is there.

00:27:28.440 --> 00:27:30.360
So you don't have to be both.

00:27:30.360 --> 00:27:34.080
You have to be in joy,
because unless and until

00:27:34.080 --> 00:27:41.700
you educate yourself fully,
the feeling of joy, the feeling of Spirit,

00:27:41.700 --> 00:27:45.360
the oneness with Spirit
will not be your own.

00:27:46.260 --> 00:27:49.500
It's like, you see, My car,
which didn't start,

00:27:49.500 --> 00:27:54.900
you see, it's a hopeless instrument,
it can't take Me up to this Chelsham Road

00:27:54.900 --> 00:27:56.820
where I have to go for such an important
thing.

00:27:56.820 --> 00:27:59.280
So what's the use of having such a car,
isn't it?

00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:01.380
That's what it is.

00:28:01.380 --> 00:28:06.000
One has to understand if this habit
of Mister X, Y, Z is like this,

00:28:06.000 --> 00:28:08.820
it doesn't take me there,
better not to have such a habit.

00:28:09.660 --> 00:28:12.720
Better not to have this kind of a
personality,

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:16.500
better not to have this mentality,

00:28:17.040 --> 00:28:21.060
better not have this kind of attitude,
better give up,

00:28:21.060 --> 00:28:25.920
it's all nonsense, I have come here,
on this earth to enjoy

00:28:25.920 --> 00:28:27.420
the bounties of God's love.

00:28:29.040 --> 00:28:35.460
So it is a very great day today
because internationally we are all

00:28:35.460 --> 00:28:36.720
celebrating My Birthday.

00:28:37.740 --> 00:28:41.640
Yesterday about ten o'clock I started
feeling

00:28:41.640 --> 00:28:43.440
the vibrations flowing

00:28:43.440 --> 00:28:51.180
and My husband told me that in Australia
the Puja must have started,

00:28:51.180 --> 00:28:55.500
and then later on, about, say,
twelve o'clock again it was in India

00:28:55.500 --> 00:28:57.000
I think, continuously,

00:28:57.000 --> 00:29:02.820
so I feel now when all over the world
My Birthday is on,

00:29:02.820 --> 00:29:06.300
even when it will finish here,
it will go to America,

00:29:06.300 --> 00:29:11.520
and all over the world twenty four hours
I'll be emitting vibrations perhaps

00:29:11.520 --> 00:29:15.660
because everywhere they are worshipping Me
and the sun is moving,

00:29:15.660 --> 00:29:18.600
twelve o'clock, they'll be all worshipping
Me.

00:29:18.600 --> 00:29:24.780
It's a great thing that such a day has
come

00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:28.860
that people are feeling it round the
world.

00:29:28.860 --> 00:29:37.320
That it is a great day
when the divine decided to start

00:29:37.320 --> 00:29:38.340
this Mahayoga.

00:29:40.020 --> 00:29:46.140
Now, for your education I was thinking
of writing a book,

00:29:46.680 --> 00:29:51.240
an article about how to educate yourself.

00:29:51.780 --> 00:29:58.740
But the problem is that when I write it
I do not want you to feel that

00:29:58.740 --> 00:30:08.400
"it is directed towards me", you see,
because you will find some identification.

00:30:08.400 --> 00:30:11.940
It's not directed towards anyone,
it's a general thing.

00:30:11.940 --> 00:30:16.740
Today you might be having that problem,
tomorrow another might be having that

00:30:16.740 --> 00:30:19.440
problem,
anybody, it's a general thing.

00:30:20.460 --> 00:30:24.480
With all your permission, if you say so,
I think I should write it down,

00:30:24.480 --> 00:30:27.480
which will help you,
which you should read impersonally,

00:30:27.480 --> 00:30:31.920
impersonally,
and that is going to, I'm sure, help you.

00:30:31.920 --> 00:30:36.180
That should be really the beginning
of My another book

00:30:36.180 --> 00:30:40.920
which I am thinking for Sahaja yogis,
that I should take to one book only

00:30:40.920 --> 00:30:41.880
for Sahaja yogis.

00:30:41.880 --> 00:30:46.080
The one I've written is for everyone,
but this one would be only for Sahaja

00:30:46.080 --> 00:30:46.580
yogis.

00:30:46.980 --> 00:30:56.820
The first one chapter would be:
how to educate yourself to be in Sahaja

00:30:56.820 --> 00:30:57.180
Yoga

00:30:57.180 --> 00:31:03.300
and to grow in it
and not to be deluded by ego and superego.

00:31:04.800 --> 00:31:11.640
I hope I have your permission today,
and I'll start that thing for you.

00:31:14.460 --> 00:31:17.100
Now, if there are any questions we should
ask

00:31:17.100 --> 00:31:18.780
because we have reached the point

00:31:18.780 --> 00:31:20.580
where we can start the puja now.

00:31:21.120 --> 00:31:25.560
You should know that another cleverness
your Mother has, you see,

00:31:25.560 --> 00:31:28.800
maybe the car was failed
because of Me perhaps, you can't say.

00:31:30.360 --> 00:31:33.300
I'm very clever at certain things
like arranging timings.

00:31:34.680 --> 00:31:47.040
You know, the thing is, we went for a…
there was a puja in… what was that place?

00:31:51.840 --> 00:31:54.900
We stayed in Lonaura. We had a puja there.

00:31:54.900 --> 00:31:58.860
And for that puja, you see,
they fixed the time at nine.

00:31:58.860 --> 00:32:01.740
As usual they fixed themselves
as if they never ask Me.

00:32:01.740 --> 00:32:05.280
Nine o'clock, puja is fixed, Mother,
come at nine.

00:32:05.280 --> 00:32:08.800
Mother should come, sit down,
"All right, do My puja."

00:32:10.320 --> 00:32:12.300
You see, at nine o'clock, imagine.

00:32:12.300 --> 00:32:15.120
I said, "All right, I'll be there."

00:32:15.120 --> 00:32:17.760
So I wouldn't go for My bath
till eleven o'clock.

00:32:17.760 --> 00:32:19.740
They were saying: "Mother, go for Your
bath."

00:32:19.740 --> 00:32:23.460
I said, "Just a minute, I'll do…"

00:32:23.460 --> 00:32:25.920
And without bath I wouldn't come for the
puja.

00:32:25.920 --> 00:32:29.820
So they said, "Why Mataji is not going?"
They were all very upset.

00:32:29.820 --> 00:32:33.240
Sit down, they were waiting and waiting
for "Why Mother has not come?"

00:32:34.380 --> 00:32:36.900
I said, "All right, I'll just go for a
bath."

00:32:36.900 --> 00:32:38.760
At eleven I went for a bath.

00:32:38.760 --> 00:32:41.580
And they were to have puja at nine, you
see.

00:32:41.580 --> 00:32:48.120
Then I came back about eleven thirty,
I came down, they started the puja.

00:32:48.120 --> 00:32:51.720
So before starting the puja I said,
"All right, now please see the panchanga."

00:32:51.720 --> 00:32:53.520
Where they write the dates, you see.

00:32:53.520 --> 00:32:57.000
There it was written till eleven o'clock
was amavasya,

00:32:57.000 --> 00:32:58.980
is the day when there is no moon.

00:32:58.980 --> 00:33:04.440
And nothing, no good work to be done
during that time, inauspicious, you see.

00:33:04.440 --> 00:33:06.900
I said, "How could I take My bath before
that?"

00:33:06.900 --> 00:33:08.880
And they were all amazed.

00:33:08.880 --> 00:33:12.180
I said, "I never read panchang,
but I know what is to be done what,

00:33:12.180 --> 00:33:14.700
and what time it is the most auspicious
time,

00:33:14.700 --> 00:33:16.860
that is the time everything else is to be
done.

00:33:16.860 --> 00:33:21.300
And you don't have any panchang today,
but you can find out about it."

00:33:21.300 --> 00:33:23.820
These things are very important,
timings are,

00:33:23.820 --> 00:33:25.920
because as I have to consult all the
deities,

00:33:25.920 --> 00:33:28.320
I have to consult all the stars,

00:33:28.320 --> 00:33:31.920
and also you know, the stars have got
all the deities on them,

00:33:31.920 --> 00:33:34.680
they're all to be consulted,
they are to be put right,

00:33:34.680 --> 00:33:37.140
the whole thing is to be geared up for
puja

00:33:37.140 --> 00:33:40.140
so that you have the maximum advantage.

00:33:40.740 --> 00:33:42.900
I have to work very hard for all these
things

00:33:42.900 --> 00:33:45.360
and it's a very big operation,

00:33:46.200 --> 00:33:49.680
so such a huge complicated operation
that you do not know.

00:33:49.680 --> 00:33:53.160
You see, when you start doing my puja
you get your vibrations, you think,

00:33:53.160 --> 00:33:55.560
"Oh, Mother has given us vibrations."
It's not so simple.

00:33:55.560 --> 00:34:00.180
It's a very-very big operation, imagine,
to get a car done is so difficult.

00:34:00.180 --> 00:34:03.300
Now here there are so many complicated
stuffs

00:34:03.300 --> 00:34:07.500
and the whole universe is involved into
it,

00:34:07.500 --> 00:34:09.720
so one has to work out very carefully.

00:34:09.720 --> 00:34:15.360
So only thing, one should have a humility,
why you don't understand Mother so much,

00:34:15.360 --> 00:34:18.600
it's all right,
we have to understand our Mother more and

00:34:18.600 --> 00:34:21.420
more,
so that education is also important.

00:34:22.260 --> 00:34:25.500
So far you have had faith in Me,
thank you very much for that,

00:34:25.500 --> 00:34:30.540
and I hope you'll have more faith in Me,
and understand Me better,

00:34:32.880 --> 00:34:36.900
why I do certain things
and why it is necessary.

00:34:36.900 --> 00:34:41.640
These cannot be rationalized
unless and until you really reach

00:34:41.640 --> 00:34:44.580
that state of rationality,
where the Spirit gives you the light

00:34:44.580 --> 00:34:45.080
to understand.

